1
00:01:31,510 --> 00:01:34,850
[Silent Tides]

2
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:37,979
[Episode 22]

3
00:01:40,870 --> 00:01:42,229
Send this letter

4
00:01:42,789 --> 00:01:44,950
to Dr. Ke Lin's clinic.

5
00:01:47,930 --> 00:01:48,640
Now?

6
00:01:48,670 --> 00:01:49,170
Yes.

7
00:01:49,210 --> 00:01:50,280
Go immediately.

8
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:52,479
Make sure you hand it to him personally.

9
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:53,490
Alright.

10
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:23,370
Sawa.

11
00:02:23,930 --> 00:02:26,960
The midnight Mass at Saint Dominic's Church
is about to start.

12
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:30,430
If you want to waste time
with Liang Yanming, that's your choice.

13
00:02:30,430 --> 00:02:32,579
As the Consul in Macau,

14
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:36,670
I have to go strengthen
Japanese-Portuguese relations.

15
00:02:50,010 --> 00:02:52,070
Our informant reported 5 minutes ago

16
00:02:52,390 --> 00:02:53,710
that Liang Yanming
is still at Kiang Wu Elementary School

17
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:55,440
and there has been no movement.

18
00:02:58,230 --> 00:02:59,620
[Invitation]

19
00:03:01,370 --> 00:03:02,880
[Kiang Wu Elementary School]

20
00:03:18,790 --> 00:03:23,520
[I have suffered hardships amid
the historic tides,]

21
00:03:24,270 --> 00:03:29,060
[Armed only with pen and sword,
four years have passed.]

22
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:34,490
[Our land is shattered
like wind-blown willowdown,]

23
00:03:35,220 --> 00:03:39,240
[My life adrift
like duckweed in the rain.]

24
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:44,210
[Fear I felt on the Panic Beach,]

25
00:03:44,990 --> 00:03:49,110
[Lonely I stand on the Lonely Sea.]

26
00:03:51,110 --> 00:03:55,900
[What man
has ever lived that will not die?]

27
00:03:56,990 --> 00:04:02,610
[Let my loyalty
shine in the pages of history.]

28
00:04:09,290 --> 00:04:10,060
Chief!

29
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,290
Chief!

30
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:17,250
Liang Yanming made a move.

31
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:24,440
He just left Kiang Wu Elementary School,

32
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:27,440
still wearing the
Government Bond Fundraising Committee armband?

33
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:30,240
Yes, our people saw it clearly.

34
00:04:31,110 --> 00:04:31,820
By the way,

35
00:04:32,170 --> 00:04:34,860
they said he was holding something red

36
00:04:34,860 --> 00:04:36,670
with gold characters,

37
00:04:36,670 --> 00:04:39,560
like an invitation
or an appointment letter.

38
00:04:40,030 --> 00:04:43,610
A red appointment letter
with gold characters?

39
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,530
An invitation?

40
00:04:51,860 --> 00:04:53,260
Saint Dominic's Church?

41
00:04:53,790 --> 00:04:55,610
Why would Liang Yanming
go to Saint Dominic's Church?

42
00:04:55,610 --> 00:04:58,210
The church
is holding Christmas Mass tonight.

43
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,820
De Solaire has invited

44
00:04:59,820 --> 00:05:02,490
representatives from
all countries and sectors in Macau.

45
00:05:02,490 --> 00:05:04,290
Liang Yanming is going there now

46
00:05:04,610 --> 00:05:07,440
wearing the armband.

47
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:09,670
He is clearly planning to burn his bridges

48
00:05:09,670 --> 00:05:12,670
and make a scene in front of everyone.

49
00:05:13,940 --> 00:05:14,820
He...

50
00:05:15,940 --> 00:05:17,910
really knows how to pick his spots.

51
00:05:18,180 --> 00:05:18,940
[Invitation]

52
00:05:18,940 --> 00:05:19,820
Chief,

53
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:22,440
what should we do?

54
00:05:22,860 --> 00:05:24,030
Since he insists on courting death,

55
00:05:24,030 --> 00:05:25,440
I can only let him have it.

56
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:26,860
Yamaguchi,

57
00:05:27,940 --> 00:05:29,110
take that gun.

58
00:05:29,530 --> 00:05:30,790
Let's go to the church.

59
00:05:31,110 --> 00:05:31,610
Yes.

60
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,760
What is responsibility?

61
00:05:39,790 --> 00:05:42,320
Responsibility is standing tall

62
00:05:43,030 --> 00:05:44,690
and facing things on your own.

63
00:05:45,820 --> 00:05:46,440
Yes.

64
00:05:47,909 --> 00:05:50,240
That's why
I had no choice but to let her go,

65
00:05:51,030 --> 00:05:52,290
the farther the better.

66
00:05:52,290 --> 00:05:54,909
Right. I'm telling you, Mary

67
00:05:56,170 --> 00:05:57,409
shouldn't have been the one who died.

68
00:05:57,409 --> 00:05:58,670
It should have been me.

69
00:05:58,670 --> 00:06:01,200
I should have been the one who died.

70
00:06:08,320 --> 00:06:09,200
Qiwen?

71
00:06:10,170 --> 00:06:10,800
Mrs. He.

72
00:06:10,820 --> 00:06:11,470
Mrs. He.

73
00:06:35,060 --> 00:06:35,620
Hello?

74
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:37,290
Hello,

75
00:06:37,290 --> 00:06:38,290
this is Qiao Yinwan.

76
00:06:38,290 --> 00:06:39,740
Is He Xian at home?

77
00:06:40,590 --> 00:06:41,610
Miss Qiao?

78
00:06:41,909 --> 00:06:42,800
Oh,

79
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,940
Xian isn't home. He went out.

80
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:46,720
What about his wife?

81
00:06:46,990 --> 00:06:48,530
She went out too,

82
00:06:48,530 --> 00:06:50,040
to find Xian.

83
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,070
Miss Qiao,

84
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:52,680
what do you need him for?

85
00:06:53,909 --> 00:06:55,050
Well, Mr. He,

86
00:06:55,050 --> 00:06:56,940
do you know where they went?

87
00:06:57,409 --> 00:06:59,040
When Qiwen went out,

88
00:06:59,090 --> 00:07:00,160
she told me

89
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:02,900
they'd be at that small bar
not far from home.

90
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:04,170
Miss Qiao,

91
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:06,560
if there really is anything you need,
just tell me.

92
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:08,060
I'll go find them for you.

93
00:07:10,670 --> 00:07:12,860
Alright then. thank you, Mr. He.

94
00:07:12,910 --> 00:07:14,110
No problem.

95
00:07:14,610 --> 00:07:15,020
Ah.

96
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,240
What?

97
00:07:19,740 --> 00:07:20,410
Qiwen,

98
00:07:20,990 --> 00:07:21,920
why are you here?

99
00:07:22,860 --> 00:07:24,320
I'm here to drink with you.

100
00:07:26,610 --> 00:07:28,060
Come on, drink up.

101
00:07:40,820 --> 00:07:42,490
I really didn't expect

102
00:07:44,110 --> 00:07:45,909
to see the three of you like this.

103
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:51,200
You're usually so smart

104
00:07:51,409 --> 00:07:53,110
and capable,

105
00:07:53,790 --> 00:07:56,490
seeming to understand everything

106
00:07:56,520 --> 00:07:58,820
and able to handle any difficulty.

107
00:08:00,110 --> 00:08:01,790
Aren't you supposed to be so impressive?

108
00:08:01,790 --> 00:08:04,910
Why is it that when it comes to women,
you all lose your heads,

109
00:08:04,910 --> 00:08:07,260
panic, blame the world,

110
00:08:07,260 --> 00:08:09,390
and drink yourselves into this state?

111
00:08:16,530 --> 00:08:17,320
Wanqi.

112
00:08:19,740 --> 00:08:21,550
Do you know why I came here today?

113
00:08:22,170 --> 00:08:23,570
Because Baixin asked you

114
00:08:24,090 --> 00:08:25,950
to help return the wedding dress.

115
00:08:27,110 --> 00:08:27,670
Yes.

116
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:31,560
Baixin did come to ask me
to help return her wedding dress.

117
00:08:33,750 --> 00:08:36,679
But it wasn't because she wanted
to break up with you,

118
00:08:36,870 --> 00:08:37,909
or because you were sending her

119
00:08:37,909 --> 00:08:39,980
abroad to study.

120
00:08:43,750 --> 00:08:44,680
On the contrary,

121
00:08:47,100 --> 00:08:48,580
she knew everything.

122
00:08:51,100 --> 00:08:51,870
Really?

123
00:08:52,530 --> 00:08:54,700
Do you really think
you could hide it from her?

124
00:08:54,700 --> 00:08:56,530
She's such a smart girl,

125
00:08:56,770 --> 00:08:58,480
and she cares about you so much.

126
00:08:58,480 --> 00:08:59,880
How could she not notice?

127
00:09:00,750 --> 00:09:02,930
She secretly copied down the names

128
00:09:02,930 --> 00:09:04,660
of the medicines you are taking

129
00:09:04,980 --> 00:09:07,310
and went to the hospital
to ask about them.

130
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,460
She knows you have tuberculosis.

131
00:09:14,290 --> 00:09:15,290
She told me that

132
00:09:15,750 --> 00:09:17,060
from now on,

133
00:09:17,100 --> 00:09:19,600
she would always stay by your side,

134
00:09:21,140 --> 00:09:23,110
cook every meal for you,

135
00:09:24,820 --> 00:09:27,750
remind you
to take your medicines and see the doctor,

136
00:09:28,220 --> 00:09:29,890
and go out with you to exercise

137
00:09:29,890 --> 00:09:31,530
and breathe fresh air.

138
00:09:37,980 --> 00:09:38,560
Yes.

139
00:09:39,330 --> 00:09:40,860
You don't have to marry her,

140
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:44,940
but she won't give up any hope

141
00:09:44,940 --> 00:09:47,190
of curing your illness.

142
00:09:58,030 --> 00:10:00,880
I know you don't want to burden Baixin,

143
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:04,320
but she's not as fragile as you think,

144
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:07,180
and she doesn't need
a man's so-called protection.

145
00:10:08,220 --> 00:10:09,150
On the contrary,

146
00:10:09,790 --> 00:10:11,580
for this love,

147
00:10:11,580 --> 00:10:12,800
she will protect you to the very end.

148
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:13,870
Do you understand?

149
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:24,030
As for you, Chang.

150
00:10:24,980 --> 00:10:26,410
Don't think

151
00:10:26,410 --> 00:10:28,700
that you helped Mary so much,

152
00:10:28,870 --> 00:10:31,730
or that you were the one
who pushed her to this point.

153
00:10:32,030 --> 00:10:33,250
That's not true.

154
00:10:33,570 --> 00:10:37,030
Mary's courage surpassed yours
by more than a hundred times.

155
00:10:39,010 --> 00:10:40,060
It was she

156
00:10:41,030 --> 00:10:44,060
who built the service station on her own.

157
00:10:44,750 --> 00:10:45,670
It was also she

158
00:10:46,980 --> 00:10:48,410
who, even with nothing,

159
00:10:48,410 --> 00:10:50,940
persisted in fighting
against the Japanese.

160
00:10:53,290 --> 00:10:55,620
If Mary's spirit is watching from heaven,

161
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,440
knowing that her sacrifice has only

162
00:10:57,440 --> 00:11:01,100
produced the useless mess
you three have become,

163
00:11:01,670 --> 00:11:02,980
how worthless would she feel?

164
00:11:02,980 --> 00:11:03,560
Right?

165
00:11:06,530 --> 00:11:10,870
What she wanted was a real man,

166
00:11:12,540 --> 00:11:14,320
a Yang Chang
who could run the service station

167
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:16,940
and avenge her.

168
00:11:43,030 --> 00:11:44,410
As for you, Xian,

169
00:11:45,410 --> 00:11:48,690
you're always afraid
you're dragging Yinwan down.

170
00:11:49,430 --> 00:11:52,090
You think she's just a girl
who plays the violin.

171
00:11:52,150 --> 00:11:54,210
But have you ever thought about this?

172
00:11:54,750 --> 00:11:55,910
The Qiao Yinwan who watched

173
00:11:55,910 --> 00:11:58,170
her brother die right before her eyes,

174
00:11:58,870 --> 00:12:02,190
yet stayed completely calm
without giving the slightest hint,

175
00:12:02,190 --> 00:12:03,910
and held off Japanese intelligence agents

176
00:12:03,910 --> 00:12:06,290
across all of Hong Kong for an entire day—

177
00:12:07,100 --> 00:12:08,560
is she really...

178
00:12:08,750 --> 00:12:09,580
really less brave

179
00:12:09,580 --> 00:12:11,240
or less responsible than you?

180
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:22,580
I am your wife.

181
00:12:26,950 --> 00:12:30,110
Every time you risk your life out there,

182
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:33,960
have I ever tried to stop you?

183
00:12:35,570 --> 00:12:37,160
It's not that I don't know

184
00:12:39,110 --> 00:12:40,460
that every time you go out,

185
00:12:40,460 --> 00:12:42,170
you might not come back.

186
00:12:45,790 --> 00:12:46,880
One wrong step,

187
00:12:47,780 --> 00:12:49,640
Father would lose his son,

188
00:12:50,660 --> 00:12:53,320
and Zai and Little Miss
would lose their father.

189
00:12:56,460 --> 00:12:58,960
I never complained once,

190
00:12:59,790 --> 00:13:00,930
because I know

191
00:13:04,560 --> 00:13:06,690
the responsibility you're carrying.

192
00:13:06,950 --> 00:13:09,260
No matter how worried

193
00:13:09,580 --> 00:13:11,430
or reluctant I feel,

194
00:13:12,770 --> 00:13:13,770
I still have to

195
00:13:14,130 --> 00:13:16,790
take good care of this family
while you're away.

196
00:13:17,380 --> 00:13:18,430
Only in this way

197
00:13:18,430 --> 00:13:21,650
can you fight without distractions.

198
00:13:34,830 --> 00:13:35,660
Qiwen,

199
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:38,200
thank you.

200
00:13:44,250 --> 00:13:45,080
Xian,

201
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:48,750
you know I understand you.

202
00:13:57,580 --> 00:13:59,170
In short,

203
00:13:59,170 --> 00:14:02,100
stop thinking of yourself
as someone else's savior.

204
00:14:03,870 --> 00:14:04,880
We women

205
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:10,040
are actually braver and stronger than you.

206
00:14:11,820 --> 00:14:12,700
Baixin,

207
00:14:12,700 --> 00:14:13,580
Mary,

208
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:14,790
and Yinwan—

209
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:17,440
they all knew what they were doing.

210
00:14:21,980 --> 00:14:23,910
If you really are men,

211
00:14:24,110 --> 00:14:26,440
then show your true strength and courage.

212
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,130
Xian.

213
00:14:32,580 --> 00:14:33,320
Quan?

214
00:14:34,390 --> 00:14:36,650
Old Master asked me to pass you a message.

215
00:14:36,940 --> 00:14:37,810
Mr. Liang

216
00:14:38,050 --> 00:14:39,290
is in danger.

217
00:14:49,820 --> 00:14:52,370
Dear brothers and sisters,

218
00:14:53,060 --> 00:14:56,530
peace belongs to those with kind hearts.

219
00:14:57,320 --> 00:14:59,750
In our hearts,

220
00:14:59,780 --> 00:15:01,150
we plant the seeds of truth and justice

221
00:15:01,150 --> 00:15:03,580
and ignite the light of love and goodwill.

222
00:15:03,580 --> 00:15:07,270
This light grants us the blessing

223
00:15:07,270 --> 00:15:12,270
of true brotherhood

224
00:15:12,270 --> 00:15:16,750
to help those in need

225
00:15:16,750 --> 00:15:19,820
and those suffering and abandoned.

226
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:27,420
[Jade and Jewelry]

227
00:16:13,530 --> 00:16:14,840
It also gives us the strength

228
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:17,100
to resist tyranny and oppression,

229
00:16:17,100 --> 00:16:20,820
so that together we can build a just…

230
00:16:23,940 --> 00:16:25,000
What's happening?

231
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:08,589
Ch-Chief.

232
00:17:09,310 --> 00:17:11,040
Something doesn't seem right.

233
00:17:16,589 --> 00:17:17,700
Liang Yanming.

234
00:17:20,130 --> 00:17:21,910
It must be Liang Yanming.

235
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:02,600
Fellow countrymen of Macau,

236
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:04,480
Merry...

237
00:18:05,650 --> 00:18:06,830
Christmas Eve.

238
00:18:08,460 --> 00:18:10,740
I am Liang Yanming,

239
00:18:10,850 --> 00:18:13,790
head of the

240
00:18:13,910 --> 00:18:15,810
Wartime Government Bond Fundraising Committee.

241
00:18:15,810 --> 00:18:17,370
Today is Christmas Eve,

242
00:18:18,040 --> 00:18:20,610
and people from all walks of life
in Macau have gathered here.

243
00:18:20,610 --> 00:18:22,330
I would like to take this opportunity

244
00:18:22,330 --> 00:18:23,870
to say a few words.

245
00:18:25,910 --> 00:18:27,890
The midnight Mass just now

246
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:29,060
was wonderful.

247
00:18:30,020 --> 00:18:32,450
It preached love and peace,

248
00:18:32,520 --> 00:18:34,090
kindness and justice,

249
00:18:35,220 --> 00:18:38,580
telling all of Macau
that we are brothers and sisters

250
00:18:38,740 --> 00:18:41,000
and should treat each other like family.

251
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:43,530
If that were truly the case,

252
00:18:44,110 --> 00:18:45,590
Macau would be

253
00:18:45,980 --> 00:18:47,570
a paradise on earth.

254
00:18:50,630 --> 00:18:52,160
But what about the reality?

255
00:18:53,540 --> 00:18:54,760
Just yesterday,

256
00:18:55,480 --> 00:18:58,780
the Portuguese Macau government,
for their own selfish interests,

257
00:18:58,780 --> 00:19:01,230
bowed to the Japanese

258
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:02,850
and brazenly banned

259
00:19:02,910 --> 00:19:06,810
the promotion
and sale of China's government bonds.

260
00:19:07,610 --> 00:19:10,530
This disregards China's interests

261
00:19:10,610 --> 00:19:14,310
and tramples on the patriotic hearts
of my fellow citizens.

262
00:19:15,070 --> 00:19:16,830
It uses so-called neutrality

263
00:19:16,830 --> 00:19:19,860
as a fig leaf for aiding the enemy.

264
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:21,930
Such petty self-interest

265
00:19:21,930 --> 00:19:24,040
and cowardly behavior.

266
00:19:24,040 --> 00:19:25,200
It shows no sense of justice

267
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:26,980
and disregards the law.

268
00:19:26,980 --> 00:19:28,280
Shameful!

269
00:19:43,700 --> 00:19:44,740
Yamaguchi.

270
00:19:49,330 --> 00:19:50,950
Let me put it this way.

271
00:19:51,240 --> 00:19:53,220
If selling out the Chinese

272
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:56,500
could really buy the Portuguese
a bit of temporary safety,

273
00:19:56,570 --> 00:19:58,410
then so be it.

274
00:19:59,170 --> 00:20:00,460
But what is the reality?

275
00:20:00,460 --> 00:20:02,220
Everyone knows

276
00:20:02,520 --> 00:20:05,310
that when bandits
are met with submission and flattery,

277
00:20:05,310 --> 00:20:07,570
they only become more ruthless

278
00:20:07,740 --> 00:20:09,820
and more greedy.

279
00:20:09,890 --> 00:20:10,820
Isn't that true?

280
00:20:11,040 --> 00:20:13,280
Looking back on Macau over the past year,

281
00:20:13,280 --> 00:20:14,410
in the face of crisis,

282
00:20:14,410 --> 00:20:17,960
when did weakness ever buy us a way out?

283
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:20,680
Every time, it was only through

284
00:20:20,680 --> 00:20:21,870
our unity and determined struggle

285
00:20:21,870 --> 00:20:24,170
that we turned danger into safety.

286
00:20:27,650 --> 00:20:29,500
There is an old Chinese saying:

287
00:20:30,260 --> 00:20:33,460
"without the lips,
the teeth will be exposed to the cold."

288
00:20:33,650 --> 00:20:34,220
Today,

289
00:20:34,630 --> 00:20:36,570
if you abandon the Chinese people,

290
00:20:36,570 --> 00:20:38,440
who make up 96 percent

291
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:39,770
of Macau's population,

292
00:20:39,890 --> 00:20:42,670
tomorrow,
when the bandits turn their knives on you,

293
00:20:42,670 --> 00:20:43,440
tell me,

294
00:20:44,150 --> 00:20:45,700
who will come to your aid?

295
00:20:45,700 --> 00:20:48,140
Who will save you from disaster?

296
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:50,570
I'm afraid by then,

297
00:20:50,570 --> 00:20:52,370
you will be nothing
but lambs on the chopping block,

298
00:20:52,370 --> 00:20:54,370
waiting to be slaughtered.

299
00:20:55,610 --> 00:20:57,110
How tragic.

300
00:20:58,960 --> 00:20:59,980
Such a shame.

301
00:21:23,590 --> 00:21:27,280
Chief, I'm in position and ready to shoot.

302
00:21:29,240 --> 00:21:31,370
Colonel Sawa, what are you doing?

303
00:21:32,630 --> 00:21:34,670
What do you think I could be doing?

304
00:21:37,940 --> 00:21:38,650
You...

305
00:21:38,810 --> 00:21:40,270
So many eyes are watching.

306
00:21:40,830 --> 00:21:41,930
Are you insane?

307
00:21:44,240 --> 00:21:45,430
Let me say

308
00:21:45,980 --> 00:21:48,380
a few more words
to my Chinese compatriots.

309
00:21:49,260 --> 00:21:50,920
Given the current situation,

310
00:21:51,070 --> 00:21:54,020
with the Japanese military threats outside

311
00:21:54,180 --> 00:21:57,150
and the Portuguese Macau government
cowering in fear inside,

312
00:21:57,150 --> 00:21:59,540
persevering in the effort
to save our country

313
00:21:59,540 --> 00:22:00,870
is no easy task.

314
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:03,930
But if we do not persevere,

315
00:22:05,480 --> 00:22:08,040
China will perish as a nation.

316
00:22:08,870 --> 00:22:11,020
So, I hereby call upon

317
00:22:11,240 --> 00:22:13,960
the 400 thousand Chinese compatriots
of Macau

318
00:22:13,960 --> 00:22:16,200
to rally your spirits

319
00:22:16,850 --> 00:22:19,000
and be ready to make sacrifices.

320
00:22:19,280 --> 00:22:21,480
I call upon every Chinese person

321
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:24,740
to unite as one and to stand together
with a single purpose,

322
00:22:25,500 --> 00:22:29,000
like countless drops of rain converging into a mighty flood.

323
00:22:29,020 --> 00:22:32,610
Then we will be able to sweep away all obstacles,

324
00:22:32,670 --> 00:22:36,500
forging an iron Great Wall
of resistance and national salvation,

325
00:22:36,500 --> 00:22:38,500
unbreakable and indestructible!

326
00:22:38,650 --> 00:22:39,480
In this way,

327
00:22:39,980 --> 00:22:42,720
our China, our magnificent China,

328
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:44,310
will become something to be celebrated

329
00:22:44,310 --> 00:22:46,310
and remembered with tears and song!

330
00:22:53,680 --> 00:22:55,670
Not only the Portuguese Macau government,

331
00:22:55,670 --> 00:22:57,940
but also people from all sectors, are present.

332
00:22:57,940 --> 00:22:59,230
Killing now

333
00:22:59,460 --> 00:23:01,230
would only backfire.

334
00:23:04,260 --> 00:23:04,940
What's happening?

335
00:23:04,940 --> 00:23:06,270
-Excuse me.
-Excuse me.

336
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:07,740
I think I saw Xian.

337
00:23:07,890 --> 00:23:10,750
Master Sanhe,
I'll go check. Please wait in the car.

338
00:23:14,830 --> 00:23:15,540
Xian!

339
00:23:15,890 --> 00:23:16,520
Xian!

340
00:23:17,720 --> 00:23:18,460
Dr. Ke?

341
00:23:18,940 --> 00:23:19,580
Make way!

342
00:23:19,600 --> 00:23:20,180
Make way!

343
00:23:20,210 --> 00:23:20,940
Make way!

344
00:23:21,260 --> 00:23:22,370
Make way!

345
00:23:22,370 --> 00:23:23,000
Excuse me.

346
00:23:23,000 --> 00:23:23,810
Make way!

347
00:23:23,810 --> 00:23:24,610
Let me through!

348
00:23:24,610 --> 00:23:25,830
I know

349
00:23:27,780 --> 00:23:29,910
that in the corners below the stage,

350
00:23:30,650 --> 00:23:32,240
hidden

351
00:23:32,890 --> 00:23:34,500
in the darkness,

352
00:23:35,180 --> 00:23:36,910
there are all kinds of monsters

353
00:23:37,240 --> 00:23:39,570
gnashing their teeth at me.

354
00:23:39,570 --> 00:23:40,630
It doesn't matter.

355
00:23:42,480 --> 00:23:43,650
I

356
00:23:43,890 --> 00:23:47,130
made up my mind long ago to die if I must.

357
00:23:49,740 --> 00:23:51,850
I want to kill one

358
00:23:53,090 --> 00:23:59,500
as a warning to the others.

359
00:24:03,040 --> 00:24:03,540
Come!

360
00:24:03,980 --> 00:24:05,200
Come on!

361
00:24:09,150 --> 00:24:09,960
Make way!

362
00:24:10,260 --> 00:24:11,280
-Excuse me!
-Excuse me!

363
00:24:11,280 --> 00:24:12,510
Make way!

364
00:24:14,170 --> 00:24:16,670
Shoot!

365
00:24:35,700 --> 00:24:37,220
Mr. Liang!

366
00:24:47,390 --> 00:24:49,960
Heaven and Earth possess righteous energy,

367
00:24:49,960 --> 00:24:52,480
flowing in myriad forms.

368
00:24:52,480 --> 00:24:54,980
Below, it becomes rivers and mountains;

369
00:24:54,980 --> 00:24:57,520
above, it becomes the sun and the stars.

370
00:24:57,520 --> 00:24:58,690
When found in man,
it's called the Noble Spirit,

371
00:24:58,690 --> 00:25:00,020
[In memory of Liang Yanming.
He has not yet been avenged]

372
00:25:00,020 --> 00:25:02,540
vast and mighty, filling the firmament.

373
00:25:02,540 --> 00:25:04,780
When the government is honest and just,

374
00:25:05,260 --> 00:25:07,760
it functions in harmony,
radiating brilliance throughout the court.

375
00:25:07,760 --> 00:25:10,310
But in times of extremity, integrity is revealed—

376
00:25:10,310 --> 00:25:11,260
each instance shines through history.

377
00:25:11,260 --> 00:25:13,070
[In memory of Liang Yanming.
He has not yet been avenged]

378
00:25:13,070 --> 00:25:15,850
In the state of Qi,
there were the historical records;

379
00:25:15,850 --> 00:25:18,540
in the state of Jin, there was
the brush of Dong Hu that upheld justice.

380
00:25:18,540 --> 00:25:21,480
In the Qin dynasty, there was Zhang Liang's iron hammer;

381
00:25:21,480 --> 00:25:24,410
in the Han dynasty,
there was Su Wu's envoy staff.

382
00:25:24,410 --> 00:25:27,240
It was also manifested
in General Yan's head;

383
00:25:27,240 --> 00:25:29,890
in the blood of Minister Ji.

384
00:25:29,890 --> 00:25:32,540
It was seen in the teeth Zhang Xun,

385
00:25:32,540 --> 00:25:34,350
and in the tongue of Yan Gaoqing.

386
00:25:34,350 --> 00:25:36,240
[Dear Ke Lin,]

387
00:25:37,070 --> 00:25:38,780
[we have been close friends
for many years,]

388
00:25:38,780 --> 00:25:40,500
[bound by deep mutual trust.]

389
00:25:41,410 --> 00:25:45,150
[Today, I'll bid you farewell,
so I'm leaving you these words.]

390
00:25:46,520 --> 00:25:48,370
[Since coming of age,]

391
00:25:48,370 --> 00:25:51,830
[I followed Dr. Sun Yat-sen
and joined the Chinese Alliance,]

392
00:25:52,430 --> 00:25:55,040
[taking the salvation of China
as my lifelong mission.]

393
00:25:55,040 --> 00:25:57,130
[And it has been more than 30 years.]

394
00:25:58,890 --> 00:25:59,350
[In memory of Liang Yanming.
He has not yet been avenged]

395
00:25:59,350 --> 00:26:02,890
[Now, with the nation in grave peril
and the Japanese invaders pressing in,]

396
00:26:02,890 --> 00:26:06,280
[our great China lies shattered.]

397
00:26:07,410 --> 00:26:11,430
[Though I long to do my small part
to save the country,]

398
00:26:11,430 --> 00:26:12,760
[I exhausted every effort]

399
00:26:12,760 --> 00:26:14,540
[yet achieved nothing of consequence.]

400
00:26:14,540 --> 00:26:17,780
[It makes me even more ashamed.]

401
00:26:21,930 --> 00:26:23,520
[I know well that]

402
00:26:23,520 --> 00:26:27,500
[the underground
multi-party supply transport network]

403
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:32,330
[you mentioned before was your idea.]

404
00:26:32,670 --> 00:26:35,350
[It is indeed the best strategy
to break the deadlock]

405
00:26:35,350 --> 00:26:36,850
[of resistance in Macau.]

406
00:26:39,890 --> 00:26:42,540
[Yet, bound by factional divisions,]

407
00:26:42,540 --> 00:26:46,090
[I stubbornly refused to accept it,
confining myself to narrow views.]

408
00:26:46,090 --> 00:26:49,700
[Such behavior can be called that
of a frog in a well, utterly foolish.]

409
00:26:49,700 --> 00:26:52,150
[At a time of national crisis,]

410
00:26:52,180 --> 00:26:52,350
[we compatriots should have stood united.]

411
00:26:52,350 --> 00:26:55,460
[Wartime Government Bond Sales Point]

412
00:26:55,460 --> 00:26:58,410
[If such unity were obstructed
by my own blindness,]

413
00:26:58,850 --> 00:27:01,540
[how could I face our people in life,]

414
00:27:01,540 --> 00:27:04,980
[or Dr. Sun in death?]

415
00:27:07,960 --> 00:27:08,890
[Fortunately, you are a man
of integrity and magnanimity,]

416
00:27:08,890 --> 00:27:11,430
[Wartime Government Bond Sales Point]

417
00:27:14,170 --> 00:27:17,900
[and I know you will not hold
my past shortsightedness against me.]

418
00:27:18,940 --> 00:27:21,230
[I've left a letter to Secretary Lin.]

419
00:27:21,720 --> 00:27:23,690
[From this day forward,]

420
00:27:23,690 --> 00:27:24,050
[the Macau Party branch
will abandon partisan barriers]

421
00:27:24,050 --> 00:27:25,780
[In memory of Liang Yanming.
He has not yet been avenged]

422
00:27:25,780 --> 00:27:28,910
[and devote itself
fully to multi-party cooperation.]

423
00:27:29,930 --> 00:27:34,460
[After my death, the overall direction
of Macau's resistance]

424
00:27:35,330 --> 00:27:37,520
[will depend on your leadership.]

425
00:27:38,590 --> 00:27:44,310
[Only then can I die without worries.]

