441
00:28:50,750 --> 00:28:51,560
No.

442
00:28:52,150 --> 00:28:54,610
Medicines only work
if you take them on time.

443
00:28:55,020 --> 00:28:55,810
Baixin.

444
00:28:57,110 --> 00:28:59,640
I've prepared the guest room across the hall.

445
00:28:59,760 --> 00:29:01,520
From now on, I'll be living there.

446
00:29:01,520 --> 00:29:02,760
I'll handle

447
00:29:02,760 --> 00:29:03,490
what you eat,

448
00:29:03,750 --> 00:29:05,010
what you wear,

449
00:29:05,700 --> 00:29:06,650
when you sleep and wake up,

450
00:29:06,650 --> 00:29:08,110
which medicines you take,

451
00:29:08,110 --> 00:29:10,040
and which treatments you undergo.

452
00:29:18,130 --> 00:29:19,080
Don't worry.

453
00:29:19,830 --> 00:29:21,940
I'll take care of you
until you get better.

454
00:29:21,940 --> 00:29:22,990
After that,

455
00:29:24,130 --> 00:29:25,730
you can do whatever you want.

456
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:27,680
Baixin.

457
00:29:33,430 --> 00:29:35,030
If I want you to take care of me

458
00:29:35,540 --> 00:29:36,800
for the rest of my life,

459
00:29:37,440 --> 00:29:38,640
would you be willing?

