485
00:32:50,740 --> 00:32:53,810
and guarantee that under his leadership,

486
00:32:53,810 --> 00:32:57,810
this station will undoubtedly
make greater contribution

487
00:32:57,810 --> 00:33:00,410
to Allied Forces' intelligence work.

