504
00:34:04,260 --> 00:34:05,860
Thank you for your hard work.

505
00:34:07,680 --> 00:34:08,810
Six and a half years.

506
00:34:10,290 --> 00:34:11,889
Exactly six and a half years.

507
00:34:13,210 --> 00:34:15,870
I finally hear someone call me "comrade" again.

508
00:34:16,900 --> 00:34:18,500
Thank you for your hard work.

509
00:34:20,710 --> 00:34:21,710
Comrade Hannian,

510
00:34:22,409 --> 00:34:23,310
tell me,

511
00:34:23,810 --> 00:34:26,270
what are the organization's instructions?

512
00:34:30,159 --> 00:34:31,889
Then I'll get straight to the point.

513
00:34:31,889 --> 00:34:33,040
There are three things.

514
00:34:33,040 --> 00:34:33,850
First,

515
00:34:34,850 --> 00:34:36,429
following your introduction last time,

516
00:34:36,429 --> 00:34:37,909
the supplies purchased

517
00:34:37,909 --> 00:34:38,730
by patriotic businessmen in Macau

518
00:34:38,730 --> 00:34:41,600
at the request
of the Hong Kong Liaison Headquarters

519
00:34:41,600 --> 00:34:44,460
have been successfully delivered
to the base in North China,

520
00:34:44,460 --> 00:34:46,210
which has greatly relieved

521
00:34:46,210 --> 00:34:48,010
the shortage of supplies there.

522
00:34:50,929 --> 00:34:52,330
I'm glad I could help the base.

523
00:34:52,330 --> 00:34:53,730
That puts my mind at ease.

524
00:34:54,909 --> 00:34:56,000
Second,

525
00:34:56,000 --> 00:34:58,500
it's about your recent performance.

526
00:34:58,500 --> 00:35:00,000
During the government bond incident,

527
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:01,270
at a critical moment,

528
00:35:01,270 --> 00:35:04,000
you stirred up patriotic enthusiasm
among the people of Macau

529
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:06,770
and galvanized anti-Japanese sentiment across all sectors.

530
00:35:06,770 --> 00:35:09,120
This played a crucial role
in the initial formation

531
00:35:09,120 --> 00:35:10,390
of Macau's

532
00:35:10,390 --> 00:35:11,990
united anti-fascist front.

533
00:35:12,620 --> 00:35:13,850
After careful consideration,

534
00:35:13,850 --> 00:35:15,060
the organization has decided

535
00:35:15,060 --> 00:35:16,710
