537
00:35:18,560 --> 00:35:19,910
Thanks for the recognition.

538
00:35:19,910 --> 00:35:20,910
I'll continue to work hard.

539
00:35:20,910 --> 00:35:21,690
Good.

540
00:35:21,890 --> 00:35:22,760
Third,

541
00:35:23,560 --> 00:35:26,040
we need to discuss the current situation in Macau

542
00:35:26,040 --> 00:35:28,330
and your future priorities.

543
00:35:28,850 --> 00:35:29,370
Okay.

544
00:35:36,520 --> 00:35:37,620
