555
00:35:57,940 --> 00:36:00,440
to transport them to Zhongshan by motor launch.

556
00:36:00,440 --> 00:36:02,850
Under the protection
of Commander Ou's guerrilla unit,

557
00:36:02,850 --> 00:36:05,790
they were successfully transferred to the rear areas.

558
00:36:05,790 --> 00:36:06,620
The price

559
00:36:08,100 --> 00:36:09,430
was fairly reasonable.

560
00:36:09,560 --> 00:36:10,500
Mr. Rodrigues,

561
00:36:10,830 --> 00:36:13,000
helping you dispose of this backlog of goods

562
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:14,140
serves both as an explanation
for the misunderstanding

563
00:36:14,140 --> 00:36:15,280
over the hijacking

564
00:36:15,390 --> 00:36:16,980
and as concrete proof

565
00:36:17,190 --> 00:36:19,230
of the underground multi-party supply transport network

566
00:36:19,230 --> 00:36:20,690
that I mentioned earlier.

567
00:36:20,830 --> 00:36:21,980
The facts are clear.

568
00:36:22,500 --> 00:36:24,030
As long as we work together,

569
00:36:24,270 --> 00:36:26,580
this line can operate successfully.

570
00:36:27,080 --> 00:36:27,810
So this time,

571
00:36:28,290 --> 00:36:29,890
Master Sanhe and I have come

572
00:36:30,120 --> 00:36:32,390
in the hope that you will set aside past grievances

573
00:36:32,390 --> 00:36:33,930
and persuade the Portuguese merchants in Macau

574
00:36:33,930 --> 00:36:35,770
to join this transport network.

575
00:36:39,730 --> 00:36:40,810
Mr. Rodrigues,

576
00:36:41,310 --> 00:36:43,620
if you're still upset

577
00:36:43,620 --> 00:36:44,820
about the hijacking,

578
00:36:45,460 --> 00:36:46,710
I, Huang Sanhe,

579
00:36:47,250 --> 00:36:48,870
representing the Tai Ho Brotherhood,

580
00:36:48,870 --> 00:36:51,480
would like to pour you tea and apologize.

581
00:36:58,930 --> 00:36:59,940
Mr. Rodrigues,

582
00:37:00,500 --> 00:37:01,020
please.

583
00:37:01,020 --> 00:37:02,190
No, no, no.

584
00:37:02,750 --> 00:37:04,270
Master Sanhe, you're too kind.

585
00:37:04,270 --> 00:37:05,190
This cup of tea

586
00:37:05,540 --> 00:37:07,070
should be mine to offer you.

587
00:37:07,580 --> 00:37:07,870
Here.

588
00:37:07,870 --> 00:37:08,480
No, no, no.

589
00:37:08,580 --> 00:37:09,910
I was in the wrong first.

590
00:37:10,020 --> 00:37:10,370
No.

591
00:37:10,370 --> 00:37:11,540
I should be the one to apologize first.

592
00:37:11,540 --> 00:37:12,560
Please, let me.

593
00:37:12,560 --> 00:37:14,360
Then let me play the peacemaker.

594
00:37:15,120 --> 00:37:16,430
Drink this cup of tea,

595
00:37:16,430 --> 00:37:18,000
the clouds will part,

596
00:37:18,000 --> 00:37:18,890
and from this day on,

597
00:37:18,890 --> 00:37:19,950
we are all friends.

598
00:37:25,620 --> 00:37:27,050
Well, the warrant...

599
00:37:27,190 --> 00:37:29,250
I'll have it withdrawn immediately.

600
00:37:31,730 --> 00:37:33,060
To sum up,

601
00:37:33,060 --> 00:37:35,050
the patriotic merchants led by Ma Wanqi and He Xian

602
00:37:35,050 --> 00:37:37,750
have become the backbone of Macau's business community.

603
00:37:37,750 --> 00:37:39,480
The Portuguese merchants have also been won over.

604
00:37:39,480 --> 00:37:40,370
As for transportation,

605
00:37:40,370 --> 00:37:41,580
Zhongshan Anti-Japanese Guerrillas

606
00:37:41,580 --> 00:37:42,940
and the Tai Ho Brotherhood, an unofficial force,

607
00:37:42,940 --> 00:37:43,960
are working together smoothly.

608
00:37:43,960 --> 00:37:46,870
Anti-Japanese sentiment across all sectors in Macau is now running high.

609
00:37:46,870 --> 00:37:47,530
Therefore,

610
00:37:47,690 --> 00:37:50,230
an underground supply transport network

611
00:37:50,230 --> 00:37:52,540
with Macau at its core is already on solid footing.

612
00:37:52,540 --> 00:37:54,390
How is the Allied Forces' intelligence station doing?

613
00:37:54,390 --> 00:37:55,980
Although it was suspended for a while,

614
00:37:55,980 --> 00:37:58,170
it has now resumed

615
00:37:58,290 --> 00:37:59,510
and is expanding.

616
00:37:59,600 --> 00:38:01,390
I found them a new location,

617
00:38:01,390 --> 00:38:02,730
right next to my clinic,

618
00:38:02,730 --> 00:38:05,060
where they can run a grocery shop as cover.

619
00:38:06,960 --> 00:38:08,490
That's a good arrangement.

620
00:38:08,940 --> 00:38:09,670
Previously,

621
00:38:10,770 --> 00:38:13,230
our Guangdong–Hong Kong resistance forces

622
00:38:13,310 --> 00:38:15,770
already cooperated with the Allied Forces on intelligence.

623
00:38:15,770 --> 00:38:17,390
Now with this intelligence station,

624
00:38:17,390 --> 00:38:18,870
Allied intelligence can now be integrated

625
00:38:18,870 --> 00:38:20,940
into our entire Guangdong–Hong Kong–Macau

626
00:38:20,940 --> 00:38:22,350
underground intelligence network.

627
00:38:22,350 --> 00:38:24,350
This also aligns with the central leadership's directive

628
00:38:24,350 --> 00:38:27,350
to strengthen the global anti-fascist united front.

629
00:38:28,540 --> 00:38:29,040
Comrade Hannian,

630
00:38:29,040 --> 00:38:31,370
what's the next focus of our work in Macau?

631
00:38:31,850 --> 00:38:32,710
Just one thing:

632
00:38:33,390 --> 00:38:34,980
to consolidate and strengthen

633
00:38:34,980 --> 00:38:37,480
the anti-fascist united front in Macau

634
00:38:37,940 --> 00:38:41,190
and accelerate the development of Macau's underground supply network.

635
00:38:41,190 --> 00:38:43,100
It must be able to support both the front lines

636
00:38:43,100 --> 00:38:45,540
and the base areas behind enemy lines,

637
00:38:45,540 --> 00:38:48,060
forming stable supply and distribution channels.

638
00:38:48,060 --> 00:38:49,500
So through Macau,

639
00:38:50,690 --> 00:38:51,980
we'll sell more specialty products

640
00:38:51,980 --> 00:38:53,910
to obtain more strategic supplies.

641
00:38:53,910 --> 00:38:54,890
Not just more,

642
00:38:54,890 --> 00:38:57,250
but ten or a hundred times more than before.

643
00:38:57,250 --> 00:38:58,940
This channel must become normalized

644
00:38:58,940 --> 00:39:00,430
and remain operational at all times.

645
00:39:00,430 --> 00:39:01,210
The significance of this for improving

646
00:39:01,210 --> 00:39:02,460
the entire enemy‑rear battlefield

647
00:39:02,460 --> 00:39:03,990
and the supply of our forces

648
00:39:04,020 --> 00:39:05,350
cannot be overstated.

649
00:39:06,430 --> 00:39:09,430
To ensure the smooth progress of this work,

650
00:39:09,430 --> 00:39:11,500
the organization has decided to transfer

651
00:39:11,500 --> 00:39:13,190
a capable comrade from Hong Kong

652
00:39:13,190 --> 00:39:14,480
to be stationed in Macau long‑term

653
00:39:14,480 --> 00:39:16,410
under the cover of a merchant.

654
00:39:16,710 --> 00:39:17,910
He will have two tasks.

655
00:39:17,910 --> 00:39:18,370
First,

656
00:39:18,750 --> 00:39:20,140
to actively bring patriotic businessmen

657
00:39:20,140 --> 00:39:23,000
such as Ma Wanqi and He Xian

658
00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:24,170
closer to our Party

659
00:39:24,350 --> 00:39:26,070
and turn them into our allies.

660
00:39:26,520 --> 00:39:27,100
Second,

661
00:39:27,270 --> 00:39:30,140
to ensure the safe operation of this supply line.

662
00:39:30,750 --> 00:39:31,350
Do you know

663
00:39:32,270 --> 00:39:33,400
who Hong Kong

664
00:39:33,830 --> 00:39:35,080
is sending this time?

665
00:39:35,270 --> 00:39:35,750
Who?

666
00:39:37,350 --> 00:39:38,610
Comrade Ke Zhengping.

667
00:39:39,250 --> 00:39:41,460
Both Hong Kong Liaison Headquarters and the East River Column

668
00:39:41,460 --> 00:39:42,250
agree that

669
00:39:42,540 --> 00:39:43,580
Comrade Zhengping

670
00:39:43,580 --> 00:39:45,380
is the most suitable candidate.

671
00:39:45,660 --> 00:39:46,600
From now on,

672
00:39:47,190 --> 00:39:49,690
you two brothers can fight side by side.

673
00:39:51,390 --> 00:39:52,100
Well,

674
00:39:52,790 --> 00:39:54,120
what about my identity?

675
00:39:54,910 --> 00:39:55,910
Here's the thing.

676
00:39:56,690 --> 00:39:57,910
Comrade Ke Zhengping

677
00:39:57,910 --> 00:39:58,930
was sent by

678
00:39:59,100 --> 00:40:02,160
East River Column and Hong Kong Liaison Headquarters.

679
00:40:02,540 --> 00:40:04,470
He's on a separate line from yours.

680
00:40:04,790 --> 00:40:05,520
Understood.

681
00:40:06,790 --> 00:40:07,250
So on the surface,

682
00:40:07,250 --> 00:40:09,310
I can only be his older brother.

683
00:40:09,710 --> 00:40:10,460
Don't rush.

684
00:40:10,850 --> 00:40:11,980
I haven't finished.

685
00:40:12,040 --> 00:40:13,900
Comrade Ke Zhengping was ordered

686
00:40:14,080 --> 00:40:15,580
to accept the leadership

687
00:40:16,430 --> 00:40:17,490
of "Buddha's Hand"

688
00:40:17,710 --> 00:40:19,440
under special circumstances.

689
00:40:19,560 --> 00:40:20,420
That means that

690
00:40:21,020 --> 00:40:21,940
in ordinary times,

691
00:40:21,940 --> 00:40:24,640
you will oversee and guide his daily work,

692
00:40:24,640 --> 00:40:26,700
and in extremely urgent situations,

693
00:40:27,350 --> 00:40:29,040
you may, in the identity of Buddha's Hand,

694
00:40:29,040 --> 00:40:30,370
issue him direct orders

695
00:40:31,290 --> 00:40:32,620
and even mobilize

696
00:40:32,620 --> 00:40:34,190
the Party's underground organizations

697
00:40:34,190 --> 00:40:36,890
and armed forces across the Guangdong‑Hong Kong‑Macau region.

698
00:40:36,890 --> 00:40:38,250
The purpose is to ensure

699
00:40:38,620 --> 00:40:40,350
the safety of this supply line.

700
00:40:42,370 --> 00:40:43,520
The code phrase for special orders

701
00:40:43,520 --> 00:40:45,060
consists of 11 words:

702
00:40:45,510 --> 00:40:46,840
The Great Way prevails;

703
00:40:47,210 --> 00:40:49,340
all under heaven belong to the people.

704
00:40:49,790 --> 00:40:51,120
The Great Way prevails;

705
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:53,610
all under heaven belong to the people.

706
00:40:54,460 --> 00:40:55,260
I remembered.

707
00:40:56,190 --> 00:40:58,690
It's settled then. Next time come to my club for drinks.

708
00:40:58,690 --> 00:41:00,080
We won't leave until we're drunk!

709
00:41:00,080 --> 00:41:01,020
Don't worry.

710
00:41:01,020 --> 00:41:03,620
I, Rodrigues, will drink with you till the end.

711
00:41:04,600 --> 00:41:05,580
Mr. Rodrigues.

712
00:41:07,540 --> 00:41:08,220
Rodrigues,

713
00:41:08,330 --> 00:41:09,520
you have other guests?

714
00:41:09,520 --> 00:41:10,920
so I'll take my leave now.

715
00:41:11,330 --> 00:41:12,660
I won't see you out then.

716
00:41:19,100 --> 00:41:20,510
Well.

717
00:41:20,620 --> 00:41:21,830
Mr. Rodrigues.

718
00:41:22,100 --> 00:41:24,440
Last time, the contract we agreed on

719
00:41:24,470 --> 00:41:26,640
was unfortunately interrupted halfway through.

720
00:41:26,640 --> 00:41:27,390
Today,

721
00:41:27,500 --> 00:41:28,370
we're here

722
00:41:28,370 --> 00:41:29,640
to see whether

723
00:41:29,640 --> 00:41:31,410
we can finally sign it.

724
00:41:31,940 --> 00:41:32,640
Sorry.

725
00:41:32,640 --> 00:41:33,460
You're too late.

726
00:41:33,460 --> 00:41:35,520
That shipment has already been sold.

727
00:41:36,790 --> 00:41:37,210
From now on,

728
00:41:37,210 --> 00:41:38,660
all my goods

729
00:41:38,660 --> 00:41:39,980
are already spoken for.

730
00:41:39,980 --> 00:41:41,750
There's no need for you to waste your time here.

731
00:41:41,750 --> 00:41:42,370
See you.

732
00:41:45,210 --> 00:41:46,460
Gentlemen, please.

733
00:41:54,980 --> 00:41:56,230
Bastard!

734
00:41:58,520 --> 00:42:02,720
We finally managed to drive a wedge between the Portuguese and the Chinese,

735
00:42:03,730 --> 00:42:04,830
but you insisted

736
00:42:04,830 --> 00:42:06,910
on going your own way.

737
00:42:07,690 --> 00:42:09,190
Now look.

738
00:42:09,190 --> 00:42:10,330
With the bullet

739
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:12,310
that struck Liang Yanming,

740
00:42:12,370 --> 00:42:14,500
all our efforts have gone to waste!

741
00:42:14,710 --> 00:42:16,430
How do you plan to fix this?

742
00:42:17,330 --> 00:42:19,660
Increase the seizures against Portuguese merchants in Macau.

743
00:42:19,660 --> 00:42:21,600
Keep applying greater pressure

744
00:42:21,600 --> 00:42:23,600
to force the Portuguese to change their stand.

745
00:42:23,600 --> 00:42:24,730
What?

746
00:42:25,430 --> 00:42:27,660
What nonsense are you talking about?

747
00:42:29,310 --> 00:42:31,310
Across the entire Pacific Theater,

748
00:42:31,310 --> 00:42:34,690
the Empire is already at a complete disadvantage.

749
00:42:34,690 --> 00:42:36,600
What we lack now is supplies!

750
00:42:36,600 --> 00:42:37,880
Supplies!

751
00:42:39,830 --> 00:42:42,760
To maintain Japanese–Portuguese trade relations,

752
00:42:42,930 --> 00:42:44,890
Headquarters has ordered

753
00:42:45,330 --> 00:42:48,540
that all goods confiscated from Portuguese merchants

754
00:42:48,540 --> 00:42:50,540
be returned immediately without conditions!

755
00:42:50,540 --> 00:42:54,190
Similar actions will not be permitted in the future!

756
00:42:54,840 --> 00:42:56,050
Are you listening?

757
00:42:56,520 --> 00:42:57,450
So that means...

758
00:42:58,080 --> 00:43:00,600
those Portuguese don't have to pay any price at all

759
00:43:00,600 --> 00:43:04,580
for tolerating the Chinese?
